usage: prepare_humanize_long_document.py [-h] --output OUTPUT
                                         [--scene {AUTO,GENERAL,COURSE,MODELING,RESEARCH}]
                                         [--intensity {BALANCED,LIGHT,STRUCTURAL}]
                                         [--structural-transaction-scope {ADJACENT_PAIR,NONE}]
                                         [--max-author-chars MAX_AUTHOR_CHARS]
                                         [--max-lines MAX_LINES]
                                         [--min-author-chars MIN_AUTHOR_CHARS]
                                         [--voice-profile VOICE_PROFILE]
                                         [--voice-profile-sha256 VOICE_PROFILE_SHA256]
                                         [--voice-manifest VOICE_MANIFEST]
                                         [--voice-sample-spec VOICE_SAMPLE_SPEC]
                                         [--voice-allowed-root VOICE_ALLOWED_ROOT]
                                         [--editable-style-wrapper {emph,textbf,textit}]
                                         inputs [inputs ...]

冻结长 MD/TEX 输入并生成 manifest、保护占位块和初始覆盖账本；不修改源文。

positional arguments:
  inputs                一个或多个主文件或目录

options:
  -h, --help            show this help message and exit
  --output OUTPUT       必须为空的新输出目录
  --scene {AUTO,GENERAL,COURSE,MODELING,RESEARCH}
  --intensity {BALANCED,LIGHT,STRUCTURAL}
                        冻结本轮改写权限；STRUCTURAL 会生成逐段结构清单并要求结构映射包
  --structural-transaction-scope {ADJACENT_PAIR,NONE}
                        生成候选型跨 unit 事务清单；ADJACENT_PAIR 仅接受
                        STRUCTURAL，且不授予执行或语义放行权限
  --max-author-chars MAX_AUTHOR_CHARS
  --max-lines MAX_LINES
  --min-author-chars MIN_AUTHOR_CHARS
  --voice-profile VOICE_PROFILE
  --voice-profile-sha256 VOICE_PROFILE_SHA256
  --voice-manifest VOICE_MANIFEST
  --voice-sample-spec VOICE_SAMPLE_SPEC
  --voice-allowed-root VOICE_ALLOWED_ROOT
  --editable-style-wrapper {emph,textbf,textit}
                        显式授权移除的非语义 TeX 样式包装命令；可重复，默认全部保护
